ORIGINAL PCMCIA SCRIPTS

       If you are using the original configuration  scripts  from  the  Pcmcia
       package, you can use this method.

       File : /etc/pcmcia/wireless.opts

       Form : *,*,*,*)
                  ESSID="Home"
                  MODE="Ad-Hoc"
                  ;;

       See also :
              /etc/pcmcia/wireless
              File PCMCIA.txt part of Wireless Tools package


